{"tid":879844,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"話說啱啱有幾個中國人黎問路，我好熱情咁為佢解答","createTime":"2018-10-28T10:08:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T05:05:20.000Z","uid":1834,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5b5e5a30552a12fb21ccb287a8224f649dd2a8a6","tid":879844,"uid":1834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T10:08:03.000Z","msg":"話說啱啱等緊車<br />\n分別有兩個同三個中國人黎問我A11邊度搭<br />\n我用唔咸唔淡嘅中國話問佢係咪去機場，佢話想去港豬澳大橋喎<br />\n<br />\n我非常感動，<br />\n估唔到呢項大規模殺傷力建設竟然咁吸引佢地<br />\n唔識路嘅我馬上上網幫佢搵邊度有得搭呢架A11<br />\n如果唔係約左人食飯我直頭送埋佢地上車添啊<br />\n<br />\n我幫到來自中國嘅傻閪<br />\n我非常之滿足<br />\n希望佢地今晚12點前返到屋企啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/28/180658_3d82216a0e6a24fd0ab5670b2af206bf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F28%2F180658_3d82216a0e6a24fd0ab5670b2af206bf.png&h=7dd5fd56&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e9d9cd77fc6a172e696184d63ccc0a038ce97d4","tid":879844,"uid":162324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T18:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013e24343e6bd287b9b8e027e7fb1d9448c115a0","tid":879844,"uid":102132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:51:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2325b02ce1878cab473d43e3fb1254ef839cac1a","tid":879844,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T05:05:20.000Z","msg":"多謝傷港<br />\n又有叫雞錢仲可以運一大筆去外國"}]}